title_detail.value: The Power of Collaboration in the Age of AI - Philippe Humeau

entries.author: Breaking Into Cybersecurity
entries.summary:
Guests: Philippe Humeau

In this episode of Breaking Into Cybersecurity, host Philippe Humeau shares his journey from a childhood gamer in the 80s to a leading cybersecurity expert. Philippe dives into his early years of cracking games, his transition to professional IT and cybersecurity roles, and his experience in founding a company right after school. He also discusses the critical differences between Red Team and Blue Team roles, the evolving landscape of red team automation and AI, and the importance of collaboration in solving complex cybersecurity challenges. Tune in for valuable insights and practical advice for aspiring cybersecurity professionals.


Sponsored by CPF Coaching LLC - http://cpf-coaching.com

Philippe dives into his early years of cracking games, his transition to professional IT and cybersecurity roles, and his experience in founding a company right after school. He also discusses the critical differences between Red Team and Blue Team roles, the evolving landscape of red team automation and AI, and the importance of collaboration in solving complex cybersecurity challenges. Tune in for valuable insights and practical advice for aspiring cybersecurity professionals.


Sponsored by CPF Coaching LLC - http://cpf-coaching.com

The Breaking into Cybersecurity: It’s a conversation about what they did before, why did they pivot into cyber, what the process was they went through Breaking Into Cybersecurity, how they keep up, and advice/tips/tricks along the way.

The Breaking into Cybersecurity Leadership Series is an additional series focused on cybersecurity leadership and hearing directly from different leaders in cybersecurity (high and low) on what it takes to be a successful leader. We focus on the skills and competencies associated with cybersecurity leadership and tips/tricks/advice from cybersecurity leaders.
